title: Calcaires siliceux de Dole
text: The Calcaires siliceux de Dole is a <a href="Formation%20%28geology%29">geologic formation</a> in <a href="France">France</a>. It preserves <a href="fossils">fossils</a> dating back to the <a href="Jurassic">Jurassic</a> <a href="Period%20%28geology%29">period</a>.
